# project architecture
> FSD Architecture
src/
 |- app/
 |   |- route/
 |   |    ∟- [페이지경로]/ 
 |   |
 |   |- main.tsx
 |   |- index.css
 |   ∟- index.html
 |
 |- entities/
 |   ∟- [엔티티명]/           (예: post/, user/ )
 |         |- model/        (예: Post, PostComment, User)
 |         |- api/        (예: usePost, usePostCommnet, useUser)
 |         ∟- type/       (예: Post, PostComment, User)
 |
 |- features/
 |   ∟- [기능명]/             (예: post/, auth/ )
 |         |- ui/           (예: PostCard, PostHeader, PostBody, PostList, LoginForm)
 |         |- api/        (예: usePost, usePostCommnet, login, use)
 |         ∟- type/       (예: Post, PostComment)
 |
 ∟- shared/
     |- components
     |     ∟- ui
     |- api
     |- utils
     ∟- types
